<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Abraham's Blog</title><link>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/</link><description/><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 01 Jan 2023 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.inshomepgup.com/tags/ts/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>ts2</title><link>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/programming/language/typescript/%E4%BA%8C%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E5%80%BC%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E8%81%94%E5%90%88%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E4%BA%A4%E5%8F%89%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 Jan 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/programming/language/typescript/%E4%BA%8C%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E5%80%BC%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E8%81%94%E5%90%88%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E4%BA%A4%E5%8F%89%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B/</guid><description>&lt;p>ts是描述一个数据的形状。
js有那些数据，numeber啊，string啊。
也有array，map，object。&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="描述一个object的形状">描述一个object的形状。
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>用interface&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">7
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-ts" data-lang="ts">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kr">interface&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">PersonDto&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">name&lt;/span>: &lt;span class="kt">string&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">age&lt;/span>: &lt;span class="kt">number&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">job?&lt;/span>:&lt;span class="kt">string&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">salary?&lt;/span>:&lt;span class="kt">number&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="kr">readonly&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">gender&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">?:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="mi">0&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">|&lt;/span>&lt;span class="mi">1&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>语法
readonly [key]?:value
readonly 和 ? 都是可选项&lt;/p>
&lt;p>? 代表可选变量，就是这个对象的形状里，这个属性是可选的
readonly 表示这个形状里，这个属性是不可变更的&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">8
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">用type (不推荐)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">```ts
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">type PersonDto = {
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> name: string
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> age: number
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="object-类型">object 类型
&lt;/h3>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-ts" data-lang="ts">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">// object 类型
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kr">const&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">obj&lt;/span>:&lt;span class="kt">object&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">foo&lt;/span>:&lt;span class="kt">12&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>object 可以使用一些Object的函数&lt;/p></description><category>Typescript</category><category>ts</category></item><item><title>ts常用的原始数据类型</title><link>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/programming/language/typescript/%E4%B8%80%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84ts%E5%8E%9F%E5%A7%8B%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 Jan 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/programming/language/typescript/%E4%B8%80%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84ts%E5%8E%9F%E5%A7%8B%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B/</guid><description>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">7
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-ts" data-lang="ts">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kr">const&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">numA&lt;/span>: &lt;span class="kt">number&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">0&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kr">const&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">str&lt;/span>: &lt;span class="kt">string&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;&amp;#39;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kr">const&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">boo&lt;/span>: &lt;span class="kt">boolean&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kc">false&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kr">const&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">obj&lt;/span>: &lt;span class="kt">null&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kc">null&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kr">const&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">u&lt;/span>: &lt;span class="kt">undefined&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kc">undefined&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kd">function&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">abc&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">()&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="k">void&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{}&lt;/span> &lt;span class="c1">// void
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">console&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">log&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">u&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">numA&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">str&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">boo&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">obj&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">abc&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>void常用与函数的返回值。
null,undefined,常用于联合类型。
null，还没声明的object的类型。
undefined，不知道有什么用。&lt;/p></description><category>Typescript</category><category>ts</category></item></channel></rss>